description:
The Crooked North - 10pm
...Capture the gritty soul of Americana and the grinding drive of bluegrass with complex arrangements and haunting harmonies. 
www.thecrookednorth.com

Special Guests
Tough Old Bird - 9pm
...Play modern folk music that reflects the landscape it comes from, a place where the last train just pulled out and the carnival is always on its way to the next town.
www.tougholdbirdmusic.com

Doors at 7, music at 9. $7 cover
name: The Crooked North wsg Tough Old Bird
